abstract: Fans of Christopher Guest may recognize his signature style in two new music videos released on Monday, but not the products that the videos are pitching.
snippet: Fans of Christopher Guest may recognize his signature style in two new music videos released on Monday, but not the products that the videos are pitching.
lead_paragraph: Christopher Guest, the actor, writer and director famous for spoofs like “This Is Spinal Tap,” “A Mighty Wind” and “Best in Show,” has two music videos coming out today.

headline.main: Computer Support, Can You Rock to This?
headline.print_headline: Computer Support, Can You Rock to This?

abstract: Intel downplays its Viiv brand for chips after no one found its home entertainment ideas much fun.
snippet: Intel downplays its Viiv brand for chips after no one found its home entertainment ideas much fun.
lead_paragraph: There were two things wrong with Intel’s Viiv brand: First, it was almost impossible to figure out what it meant. And second, what it did mean wasn’t worth much and was hardly related to chips.

headline.main: Intel Loses Its Will to Viiv
